Fast and Accurate Heat
This electric soldering iron kit heats up quickly and precisely. The accuracy is about ±5℃
Upgraded Version
A: Better Heat Dissipation. The soldering tips with four ventilation holes and steel-pipe design help cool fast
B: Easier to Use. Adding an ON/OFF switch, you can turn the soldering iron on/off with ease

Peak Power:60W. When you adjust the temperature to 200℃, the rated power is about 5W. If you turn it to 450℃, the rated power will reach 23W. 
When you adjust the temperature to 250-400℃, there are about 30℃ errors between actual temperature and displayed temperature. And if you adjust it to 200℃ or 450℃, the displayed temperature is in line with actual temperature.
 

Feature
ON/OFF Switch: With ON/OFF switch, this soldering iron can be turned on/off easily to save energy and ensure safe welding. LED indicator will be a good hint to avoid burning by accidental
Heat Up Quickly: The 60w soldering iron heats up very fast with inner-heated ceramic induction technology and has a temperature dial with range of 200℃ to 450℃ for you to adjust temp easily
Better Heat Dissipation: Steel-pipe design helps cool fast. The four ventilation holes on the solder tip provide better heat dissipation than others. Upgraded PCBA with Chip Fixed Resistor also helps dissipate heat quickly
Excellent Product Experience: The heat-insulated silicon handle on soldering iron provides comfortable and secure grip. A decent cable length for convenient use
More Accessories: Come with 5 PCS interchangeable tips for various types of jobs, A soldering stand for heat dissipation, Solder wire( 1mm in diameter, melting point: 183℃)
 

How to use?
Step 1. Clean the electronic components to be soldered
Step 2.Once iron reaches temperature(not too high, recommend 300°C)
Step 3. Apply a little solder to the heated iron tip to prevent oxidation, then rub the iron tip to evenly extend the solder to the surface of the iron tip
Step 4. Start to solder

item_name: Night splint dorsal treatment plantar fasciitis achillies tendonitis UK NEW On Sale
item_description:
This BodyTec Wellbeing™  Night splint is used to help ease the following:

Plantar fasciitis
Achilles Tendonitis

Wear at night for effective treatment of Plantar Fasciitis - particularly helpful to reduce the pain of the first steps after getting out of bed.

The flexible shell extends from the back of the Calf, around the heel and under the sole of the foot. It's fully lined for comfort and has two adjustable straps between the Calf and sole of the foot which, when tightened, pull the toes up towards the shin. This 'dorsiflexed' position stretches the tissue of the sole of the foot known as the Plantar Fascia.

When this stretch is sustained for a prolonged period (e.g. overnight) the Plantar Fascia is held in a better position for healing. Research has shown that night splinting is effective in relieving symptoms in over 80% of cases of Plantar Fasciitis.

The Body-Tec Plantar Fasciitis Night Splint comes with a removable liner which has been designed in a way that allow the leg to sit perfect inside and and to stop creasing.Extra stitching on the liner allows leg to mould in to the foam for improved comfort.

item_name: Arduino UNO R3 Development Breadboard Microcontroller MEGA328P ATMEGA16U2 Compat On Sale
item_description:
Description

Microprocessor : MEGA328P

Operating Voltage：5V

Input Voltage（Recommend）: 7-12V

Digital I / O port：14（4 PWM Outputs）

Analog Input Port : 6

DC Current  I / O  Port：40mA

DC Current  3.3V Port : 50mA

Flash memory : 32KB (MEGA328P) （0.5kb for the boot process）

EEPROM : 1 KB (MEGA328P)

Clock Frequency :16 Hz

 

Note: There is no need to install drivers on Mac and Linux systems. (In the windows system requires IDE driver)


Product Information


This is an UNO R3 Arduino-compatible board with an atmega328p and a ch340g serial converter. 


This board is a clone to the Arduino UNO R3 but functions exactly as an Arduino and is fully compatible with the Arduino Software (IDE). 


This UNO has been manufactured using the Creative Commons files provided on the Arduino website therefore it is not manufactured by Arduino but is compatible in every way and costs much less. The release of Arduino designs under creative commons licence means that this is a legitimately compatible device.


The Uno is a microcontroller board based on the ATmega328P. It has 14 digital input/output pins. Six can be used as PWM outputs and there are six analog inputs. It has a16 MHz quartz crystal, a USB connection, a power jack, an ICSP header and a reset button. 


Contains everything needed to support the microcontroller connect it to a computer with a USB cable or power it with a AC-to-DC adapter or battery to get started.


The bootloader is already burned onto the chip so it works right out of the box in 95% of cases, just plug it in! For the other 5% install the driver located at HERE For Windows Or HERE For MAC.

 
Package Including

    1 x Board
    1 x USB cable

Installation Steps:

1. Clean and dry the wall. Make sure there is no dust or grease. 

2. Mark the position for installation on the wall.

3. Squeeze the Wangel glue onto the metal part on the back.

4. Remove the protective film from the 3M adhesive strip.

5. Install the product in the marked position and press firmly for 5-8 seconds. Do not move the product again after installation.

6. The product should not be used for 24 hours (3-5 days would be better) until the glue is dry.



Precautions:

1. Do not install this product on painted walls, wallpaper or other breathable or bumpy walls.

2. If the glue overflows, wait for it to solidify before scraping off it by knife.

3. If the installation environment is humid, the glue's setting time will be prolonged. Please wait for 48 hours or more before use.

item_name: Night splint dorsal treatment plantar fasciitis achillies tendonitis UK NEW
item_description:
This BodyTec Wellbeing™  Night splint is used to help ease the following:

Plantar fasciitis
Achilles Tendonitis

Wear at night for effective treatment of Plantar Fasciitis - particularly helpful to reduce the pain of the first steps after getting out of bed.

The flexible shell extends from the back of the Calf, around the heel and under the sole of the foot. It's fully lined for comfort and has two adjustable straps between the Calf and sole of the foot which, when tightened, pull the toes up towards the shin. This 'dorsiflexed' position stretches the tissue of the sole of the foot known as the Plantar Fascia.

When this stretch is sustained for a prolonged period (e.g. overnight) the Plantar Fascia is held in a better position for healing. Research has shown that night splinting is effective in relieving symptoms in over 80% of cases of Plantar Fasciitis.

The Body-Tec Plantar Fasciitis Night Splint comes with a removable liner which has been designed in a way that allow the leg to sit perfect inside and and to stop creasing.Extra stitching on the liner allows leg to mould in to the foam for improved comfort.

item_name: Arduino UNO R3 Development Breadboard Microcontroller MEGA328P ATMEGA16U2 Compat
item_description:
Description

Microprocessor : MEGA328P

Operating Voltage：5V

Input Voltage（Recommend）: 7-12V

Digital I / O port：14（4 PWM Outputs）

Analog Input Port : 6

DC Current  I / O  Port：40mA

DC Current  3.3V Port : 50mA

Flash memory : 32KB (MEGA328P) （0.5kb for the boot process）

EEPROM : 1 KB (MEGA328P)

Clock Frequency :16 Hz

 

Note: There is no need to install drivers on Mac and Linux systems. (In the windows system requires IDE driver)


Product Information


This is an UNO R3 Arduino-compatible board with an atmega328p and a ch340g serial converter. 


This board is a clone to the Arduino UNO R3 but functions exactly as an Arduino and is fully compatible with the Arduino Software (IDE). 


This UNO has been manufactured using the Creative Commons files provided on the Arduino website therefore it is not manufactured by Arduino but is compatible in every way and costs much less. The release of Arduino designs under creative commons licence means that this is a legitimately compatible device.


The Uno is a microcontroller board based on the ATmega328P. It has 14 digital input/output pins. Six can be used as PWM outputs and there are six analog inputs. It has a16 MHz quartz crystal, a USB connection, a power jack, an ICSP header and a reset button. 


Contains everything needed to support the microcontroller connect it to a computer with a USB cable or power it with a AC-to-DC adapter or battery to get started.


The bootloader is already burned onto the chip so it works right out of the box in 95% of cases, just plug it in! For the other 5% install the driver located at HERE For Windows Or HERE For MAC.

    1 x Board
    1 x USB cable

item_name: Heater Blower Motor Resistor For Peugeot 307 307cc 206 206cc Citroen C3 6450JP
item_description:
Description
OEM quality heater resistor/control module to repair broken heating in cars. Comes with 3 Year Warranty.
Cut out the middle-man and buy direct from ServiceX LTD, the sole UK & Europe distributor for SmartSense products.

Branded Parts at Unbranded Prices!


Compatibility
Peugeot 206 (1999-2010) - Vehicles with Single/Manual Air Conditioning only
Peugeot 307 (2001-2008) - Vehicles with Single/Manual Air Conditioning only
Citroen C3 (2002-2010) - Vehicles with Single/Manual Air Conditioning only Since MAD 0955578. For Automatic/Regulated Air Condition SEE HERE

Citroen Xsara Picasso - Vehicles with Single/Manual Air Conditioning only from MAD 0882078 until MAD 1007278

 
Symptoms of a Blown Resistor
A faulty resistor can cause a number of problems with the heating/HVAC system of a car, including but not limited to:
- No hot air 
- Heating only working intermittently
- Heating only working on some settings (when the resistor is bypassed) 

Installation
There are numerous guidelines and instructions on owner forums, the internet and on YouTube. However as this is a service part we recommend installation by a qualified professional. 

When installed it is IMPERATIVE to monitor the temperature of the resistor on first use. Sometimes a blown resistor can be a symptom of the problem and not the problem itself, and replacing it in this scenario will only cause it to blow again. If the resistor starts heating very quickly and getting too hot IMMEDIATELY SWITCH OFF YOUR CAR and diagnose the problem elsewhere. Resistors usually blow when they get too hot and this happens when too much current is being drawn from then. This can happen if there is an issue with the blower motor or even the ignition system, or a fault with the wiring. Also please check your fan is not jamming because of dirt or grease build up, or a failure in the bearings. This will also cause the fan to try to draw more power in an attempt to spin, causing the resistor to overheat and fail.

If replacing the resistor (and it is not getting hot) your heater still does not work, please check the thermo fuse or carry out further diagnosis elsewhere for a fault.

item_name: Set of 5 Round, Bent, Snipe Pliers, End and Side Cutters Jewellery Making Tools
item_description:
Description:

In each set of 5 there are the following tools;

Round Nose Pliers: They are used to bend thin metal or metal wire to make perfect circles. Great for wire projects and making double looped beads.
Bent Nose Pliers: They have a bent head as depicted in the photos. They can be used to open or close jump rings and bend wire.
Snipe Nose Pliers: They can be used to open and close Jump Rings/ Split Rings and hold small jewellery components. They can also be used for wire wrapping and making multi-diameter loops on head and eye pins.
End Cutting Pliers: They can be used to trim excess material and leave a clean, flat surface behind. They feature a bladed tip (as opposed to bladed jaws like diagonal cutters), which lets you cut close against a surface.
Wire Side Cutters: They can be used to get a flush cut on wire. They allow the flush cut even in the tightest of places, creating less filing.
Each tool has a rubber handle. A wonderful set of making tools.

item_name: Heater/Blower Motor Fan Resistor for Peugeot 206 /Citroen Xsara Picasso 6450EP
item_description:
Description

1. Color: Blue+Silver

2. Package box size: about 58mm(L) x 53mm(W) x 63mm(H)

3. Pin Number: 6 Pins

4. Interchangeable Part Numbers: 6450EP (6450.EP)

5. Installation: We recommend installation by a qualified professional.

    - When installed it is IMPERATIVE to monitor the temperature of the resistor on first use.

    - Sometimes a blown resistor can be a symptom of the problem and not the problem itself, and replacing it in this               scenario will only cause it to blow again.

    - If the resistor starts heating very quickly and getting too hot IMMEDIATELY SWITCH OFF YOUR CAR and diagnose            the problem elsewhere.

    - Resistors usually blow when they get too hot and this happens when too much current is being drawn from then.              This can happen if there is an issue with the blower motor or even the ignition system, or a fault with the wiring.

    - Also please check your fan is not jamming because of dirt or grease build up, or a failure in the bearings. This will             also cause the fan to try to draw more power in an attempt to spin, causing the resistor to overheat and fail.

      If replacing the resistor (and it is not getting hot) your heater still does not work, please check the thermo fuse or             carry out further diagnosis elsewhere for a fault.


6. Fitment:

For Peugeot 206 CC (2000+)

For Peugeot 206 Hatchback (1998-2008)

For Peugeot 206 SW Estate (2002-2008)

For Citroen Xsara Picasso N68 MPV (1999-2007)

For Citroen C5 III

Package Includes

1 x Citroen Fan Resistor

Package Includes:

     1x 4 Wire Regulator Rectifier + 1x Wiring Diagram

 

4 Wire Regulator Rectifier is Suitable for...

most Motorcycles with a carburettor based fuel system. Also suitable for classic bike conversions with a 2-phase stator coil.


A 2 phase combined full wave bridge rectifier and 12V DC motorcycle voltage regulator with 4 wires. Suitable for most motorbikes, scooters and quads and even complete classic bike conversions.

Works with kick or electric start engines. If you've only got a kick start you can even throw out your battery and run your electrics solely from this combined unit.

Motorcycle regulator rectifiers convert the fluctuating alternator current into 12Volts DC. Allowing you to run your electrics and charge your battery, all in one unit!

Swap out your old unit or even convert an old two-part system. With just 4 wires, you can finally simplify your bikes electrics.

Suitable for any motorcycle with two live output wires from the alternator. The integrated full wave rectifier on each AC input makes this unit ideal for two phase systems and even single phase systems! Simply connect up your two coil wires then connect up your battery, and you're done!

Wiring your bikes charging circuit has never been so easy! The heat sink on these units is electrically isolated from the internal circuitry, making this 4 Wire regulator rectifier also ideal for positive earth set ups.

No instructions are required but we'll provide you with our own wiring diagram anyway! That's right, we'll include a free hard copy of our 4 wire regulator rectifier wiring diagram, created by our founding engineer.

Some technical knowledge may be required when connecting this unit to your electrical circuit.

>>Description

1. This pump is 100% made from food grade silicone. It is also BPA, PVC, Phthalate and Lead free. It is safe for mum and baby, reusable and 100% eco-friendly.

2. It is specially designed to collect the leaking milk while nursing on the other side. It pumps out the milk from your breast by the natural pressure. It is more gentle and pleasurable than using electronic pump that may hurt your nipples by strong suction.

3. It is also soundless while pumping.Your baby deserves to have a quiet moment instead of the noisy motor sound while nursing.

4. With its soft and ultra-light design, it is the best traveling pump you have ever found in the market. You do not have to worry about running out of the batteries or breaking the pump accidentally on traveling. Perfect for flight trip,hiking,BBQ,fishing, camping or other outdoor activities.

Capacity: 4oz / 90ml.



>>Instructions

1. Clean the pump and lid with water. Wash by hand or dishwasher (recommend to put it on the top rack of the dishwasher).

2. Sterilize the pump in boiling water for 3-5 mins, DO NOT microwave.

3. Adjust the pump and put your nipple towards the center of the pump. Squeeze the center of the pump and release it to create a suction to attach the pump to your breast.

4. That's it and let the pump do the rest.

5. Cover the pump with lid to prevent any dust to go in. (Please note that the lid is for covering purpose only and it is not 100% leakproof.) It is advised to pour the milk into the bottles or storage bags for better storage.
